div.span:
Inflicts regular damage. For the next 25 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends.
Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
rapid spin cancels this effect.

div.div: Flamestone is a fiery bundle of energy! It loves to bask in the sun & play in desert heat. Its flames sear up a whirlwind of fun!
